**Tests:**
- StubJudge-driven Evaluate end-to-end -> Evaluation whose Score (+ a wrapped EvalResult) passes EvalResult.Validate() (rubric-coherent: Kind=rubric, Value in [0,Max], Max>0, Winner/Passed/Confidence nil).
- REAL on-disk version edit: PinRubric(root,path) pins bytes A; MUTATE the rubric file to bytes B on disk; Evaluate with the A-pinned RubricRef -> ErrRubricVersionMismatch (exercises the comparability guarantee end-to-end, Opus ask).
- Rubric loading: path-escape (../x and absolute escape) -> ErrRubricLoad; missing file -> ErrRubricLoad.
- Malformed judge-output MATRIX -> ErrJudgeOutputInvalid (no panic): empty, non-JSON, unknown field, trailing data, missing value, missing max, Max<=0, Value>Max, winner-set-for-rubric, bad severity.
