**Risks:** The method-neutral JudgeResponse (A) + ordered-target materialization (B) are the load-bearing seam choices pairwise inherits — both now pinned explicitly to eval.Score's shape and the eval.go:18-28 orientation convention, so pairwise reuses Judge/JudgeRequest/JudgeResponse with NO new type. Otherwise straightforward — mirrors the proven replay.ExecRunner precedent.

